Integrate reranking as an **optional second-pass** in the xf search flow. The reranker receives the top-N semantic candidates and re-scores them using cross-encoder attention for significantly better relevance ordering.

## Search Pipeline Architecture
```
User Query
    │
    ├─ BM25 (keyword) ──────────────────────────┐
    │                                            │
    └─ Semantic (embedding) ─┐                   │
                             ▼                   ▼
                    Retrieve Top-100      Retrieve Top-100
                             │                   │
                             ▼                   ▼
                    ┌────────────────────────────────┐
                    │   Score Fusion (RRF or linear) │
                    └──────────────┬─────────────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                    ┌──────────────────────────────┐
                    │   Rerank Top-K (optional)    │
                    │   Cross-encoder attention    │
                    │   on (query, doc) pairs      │
                    └──────────────┬───────────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                           Return Top-20
```

## Implementation

### Extending SearchResult (existing struct in src/model.rs)
The existing `SearchResult` struct gains one new field:
